<s docid="LA052989-0049" num="6"> COURT PANEL CLEARS SEN.</s>

<s docid="LA052989-0049" num="7"> BIDEN OF UNIVERSITY PLAGIARISM CHARGE</s>
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>

<s docid="LA052989-0049" num="8"> From United Press International</s>
</P>
